        <title>Check</title>
        <author>
            <name>Andrew</name>
        </author>
        <link href="https://andrewflemming.net/check/"/>
        <id>https://andrewflemming.net/check/</id>

        <updated>2020-02-17T09:35:22-05:00</updated>
            <summary>
                <![CDATA[
                    I created Check in the summer of 2011, and maintained it until its retirement in 2019. Check was an iPad and iPhone list manager that was as simple as it was beautiful. Set in Futura, on simulated stacks of paper, even the most mundane lists&hellip;
                ]]>
            </summary>
        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                <p dir="ltr">I created Check in the summer of 2011, and maintained it until its retirement in 2019.</p>
<p dir="ltr">Check was an iPad and iPhone list manager that was as simple as it was beautiful. Set in Futura, on simulated stacks of paper, even the most mundane lists came to life as works of art. Finally, your lists could be beautiful. </p>
<p dir="ltr">Check would sync your lists between your devices using Apple's iCloud service. So wherever you are, you could have your shopping lists, to-do lists, bucket lists, or whatever other list you could think of. </p>
<p dir="ltr"><img class="post__image post__image--center" src="https://andrewflemming.net/media/posts/10/check-iphone.png" alt="Check iPhone" width="292" height="571"></p>
<p dir="ltr"> <img class="post__image post__image--center" src="https://andrewflemming.net/media/posts/10/check-ipad.jpg" alt="Check iPad" width="4000" height="4000"></p>
<p dir="ltr">With Check, you could email your lists to friends, families, bosses, Mothers-in-law, doctors, engineers, curling coaches ... and the list went on!</p>
<ul>
<li dir="ltr"><address>You will be amazed as Check makes you at least 6,000 times more efficient in every aspect of your day-to-day life!*</address></li>
<li dir="ltr"><address>Your jaw will feel excruciating pain, as it drops to the floor when Check makes you new friends, and gives you more power over old ones.*</address></li>
<li dir="ltr"><address>You’ll look back on your pre-Check life as a distant ghost of a reflection of a dream, as you become a stronger, smarter, faster, sexier version of yourself than you ever thought possible.*</address></li>
<li dir="ltr"><address>A mind-numbing satisfaction will take hold, when you realize that you are better than over 99% of the population* (until they buy Check as well).</address></li>
</ul>
<p dir="ltr">Check did all of these things, and more.† </p>
<address id="mcetoc_1e19ocvgp0" dir="ltr">*Results not typical</address><address id="mcetoc_1e19ocvgq1" dir="ltr">†Or maybe it did none of them ...</address>
            ]]>
        </content>
